node_2.subject: Franz Alez
node_2.description: This is Franz Alez's plan for Tuesday February 14: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, at 12:00 pm, have lunch, open the Fishing Tackle Shop at 12:00 pm and work until 6:00 pm, close the Fishing Tackle Shop at 6:00 pm and go fishing by the river until 8:00 pm, return home at 8:00 pm, have dinner at home at 8:30 pm, watch TV from 7 to 8 pm.
